	<button class="collapsible">Day 1 : Delhi - Nainital (310kms/8hrs)</button>
	<div class="content">
		<p>Upon your arrival at Delhi Railway Station/Airport, our tour representatives will drive you to Nainital. Get into the hotel and relax for sometime. Later, enjoy a boat ride at Naini Lake in the evening (At personal). Move back to the hotel for dinner.</p>
