	<button class="collapsible">Day 2 : Nainital (Local Sight Seeing)</button></button>
	<div class="content">
		<p>After your breakfast, get ready for a lake tour to Sat Tal, Bhim Tal, Naukuchia Tal. Get back to the hotel for dinner and overnight stay.</p>
	</div>

	<button class="collapsible">Day 3 : Nainital - KaUsani (120kms/5hrs)</button>
	<div class="content">
		<p>Take your breakfast and move to KaUsani via Almora. KaUsani is a beautiful destination for people who are interested to get away from the din and dust. Proceed to the hotel and refresh yourself for sometime. Ensure to visit the sunset at View Point, Gandhi Ji Ashram. Enjoy your dinner at the hotel.</p>
	</div>

	<button class="collapsible">Day 4 : KaUsani</button>
	<div class="content">
		<p>You can enjoy the whole day at your leisure or visit the local sightseeing such as Baijnath & Bageshwar. Move back to the hotel for dinner.</p>
	</div>

	<button class="collapsible">Day 5 : KaUsani - Corbett National Park (190km/6hrs)</button>
	<div class="content">
		<p>After breakfast, drive from Kasauni to Corbett National Park and visit Ranikhet. Proceed to visit the local attractions in and around Ranikhet like Chaubatia, Hairakhan Temple and Bhaludam etc. Later, drive back to Corbett National Park. You can have your dinner at the hotel.</p>
	</div>

	<button class="collapsible">Day 6 : Corbett National Park</button>
	<div class="content">
		<p>Take your breakfast in the morning. Visit the Corbett National Park and explore great fun. Corbett National Park is exactly placed in the foothills of the Himalayas. It is the residence to an array of flora and fauna. Also it is well-known for its huge inhabitants of Leopards, Tigers, and Elephants. Move back to the hotel for dinner.</p>
	</div>

	<button class="collapsible">Day 7 : Corbett - Haridwar (265 kms / 7hrs)</button>
	<div class="content">
		<p>After a quick breakfast, get out from the hotel and depart to Haridwar. After your arrival, reach the hotel and relax for sometime. Start your day by visiting the Ganga Ji ki Aarti at Har ki Pori. Get back to the hotel for dinner.</p>
	</div>

	<button class="collapsible">Day 8 : Haridwar to Mussoorie via Rishikesh ( 85kms/ 4hrs)</button>
