		<p>Following breakfast, visit Kampty fall which is 15 kms from Mussoorie on the Yamunotri Road. It is the mesmerizing and the largest water fall situated in a gorgeous valley of Mussoorie. You can take pleasure in a breathtaking ropeway tour to Gun Hill which is the second highest peak of Mussoorie with 2122 mts. The highest point offers a panoramic sight of the Himalayan ranges.</p>
	</div>

